    "The contents in the knowledge base are extracted from [7] and [8].",
    "V. CASE STUDYTo demonstrate LLMs' capability of generating code from requirements, we chose a medium-sized web project called \"SuperFrog Scheduler\".",
    "SuperFrog is the iconic horned frog mascot of Texas Christian University (TCU), known for its participation in numerous events annually, including sports, weddings, charity functions, and media appearances.",
    "To facilitate the scheduling of SuperFrog's appearances, a request management system is necessary, involving submission by customers, review by the Spirit Director, and acceptance by student performers embodying SuperFrog.",
    "A development team, consisting of five software developers, commenced work on the SuperFrog Scheduler in October 2018 and completed the project in May 2019."
